  "translations": {
    "en": "O! Hisham then admonished people of the intellect and rghbhm in the Hereafter so he said and what/not alhyah worldly life except l'b and lhw and lldar alakhrh good for those who they fear Allah is? fla t'qlwn O! Hisham then khwf those who not they reason 'qabh so he said Most High then dmrna alakhryn. and indeed you (pl) ltmrwn upon them msbhyn. and by night is? fla t'qlwn. and said indeed We mnzlwn 'la people of hdhh alqryh rjza from the sky bma kanwa they transgress and lqd trkna mnha a sign bynh for a people they reason",
    "ur": "اے Hisham then admonished people of the intellect اور rghbhm میں the Hereafter so he said اور what/not alhyah worldly life except l'b اور lhw اور lldar alakhrh good for those who they fear Allah is? fla t'qlwn اے Hisham then khwf those who نہیں they reason 'qabh so he said Most High then dmrna alakhryn. اور indeed you (pl) ltmrwn upon them msbhyn. اور by night is? fla t'qlwn. اور said indeed We mnzlwn 'la people of hdhh alqryh rjza سے the sky bma kanwa they transgress اور lqd trkna mnha a sign bynh for a people they reason",
    "tr": "ey Hisham then admonished people of the intellect ve rghbhm içinde the Hereafter so he said ve what/not alhyah worldly life except l'b ve lhw ve lldar alakhrh good for those who they fear Allah is? fla t'qlwn ey Hisham then khwf those who değil they reason 'qabh so he said Most High then dmrna alakhryn. ve indeed you (pl) ltmrwn upon them msbhyn. ve by night is? fla t'qlwn. ve said indeed We mnzlwn 'la people of hdhh alqryh rjza -den the sky bma kanwa they transgress ve lqd trkna mnha a sign bynh for a people they reason",
    "fa": "ای Hisham then admonished people of the intellect و rghbhm در the Hereafter so he said و what/not alhyah worldly life except l'b و lhw و lldar alakhrh good for those who they fear Allah is? fla t'qlwn ای Hisham then khwf those who نه they reason 'qabh so he said Most High then dmrna alakhryn. و indeed you (pl) ltmrwn upon them msbhyn. و by night is? fla t'qlwn. و said indeed We mnzlwn 'la people of hdhh alqryh rjza از the sky bma kanwa they transgress و lqd trkna mnha a sign bynh for a people they reason",
    "id": "wahai Hisham then admonished people of the intellect dan rghbhm di dalam the Hereafter so he said dan what/not alhyah worldly life except l'b dan lhw dan lldar alakhrh good for those who they fear Allah is? fla t'qlwn wahai Hisham then khwf those who tidak they reason 'qabh so he said Most High then dmrna alakhryn. dan indeed you (pl) ltmrwn upon them msbhyn. dan by night is? fla t'qlwn. dan said indeed We mnzlwn 'la people of hdhh alqryh rjza dari the sky bma kanwa they transgress dan lqd trkna mnha a sign bynh for a people they reason",
    "bn": "হে Hisham then admonished people of the intellect এবং rghbhm মধ্যে the Hereafter so he said এবং what/not alhyah worldly life except l'b এবং lhw এবং lldar alakhrh good for those who they fear Allah is? fla t'qlwn হে Hisham then khwf those who না they reason 'qabh so he said Most High then dmrna alakhryn. এবং indeed you (pl) ltmrwn upon them msbhyn. এবং by night is? fla t'qlwn. এবং said indeed We mnzlwn 'la people of hdhh alqryh rjza থেকে the sky bma kanwa they transgress এবং lqd trkna mnha a sign bynh for a people they reason",
    "es": "oh Hisham then admonished people of the intellect y rghbhm en the Hereafter so he said y what/not alhyah worldly life except l'b y lhw y lldar alakhrh good for those who they fear Allah is? fla t'qlwn oh Hisham then khwf those who no they reason 'qabh so he said Most High then dmrna alakhryn. y indeed you (pl) ltmrwn upon them msbhyn. y by night is? fla t'qlwn. y said indeed We mnzlwn 'la people of hdhh alqryh rjza de the sky bma kanwa they transgress y lqd trkna mnha a sign bynh for a people they reason",
    "fr": "ô Hisham then admonished people of the intellect et rghbhm dans the Hereafter so he said et what/not alhyah worldly life except l'b et lhw et lldar alakhrh good for those who they fear Allah is? fla t'qlwn ô Hisham then khwf those who non they reason 'qabh so he said Most High then dmrna alakhryn. et indeed you (pl) ltmrwn upon them msbhyn. et by night is? fla t'qlwn. et said indeed We mnzlwn 'la people of hdhh alqryh rjza de the sky bma kanwa they transgress et lqd trkna mnha a sign bynh for a people they reason",
    "de": "o Hisham then admonished people of the intellect und rghbhm in the Hereafter so he said und what/not alhyah worldly life except l'b und lhw und lldar alakhrh good for those who they fear Allah is? fla t'qlwn o Hisham then khwf those who nicht they reason 'qabh so he said Most High then dmrna alakhryn. und indeed you (pl) ltmrwn upon them msbhyn. und by night is? fla t'qlwn. und said indeed We mnzlwn 'la people of hdhh alqryh rjza von the sky bma kanwa they transgress und lqd trkna mnha a sign bynh for a people they reason",
    "ru": "о Hisham then admonished people of the intellect и rghbhm в the Hereafter so he said и what/not alhyah worldly life except l'b и lhw и lldar alakhrh good for those who they fear Allah is? fla t'qlwn о Hisham then khwf those who не they reason 'qabh so he said Most High then dmrna alakhryn. и indeed you (pl) ltmrwn upon them msbhyn. и by night is? fla t'qlwn. и said indeed We mnzlwn 'la people of hdhh alqryh rjza из the sky bma kanwa they transgress и lqd trkna mnha a sign bynh for a people they reason",
    "zh": "啊 Hisham then admonished people of the intellect 和 rghbhm 在 the Hereafter so he said 和 what/not alhyah worldly life except l'b 和 lhw 和 lldar alakhrh good for those who they fear Allah is? fla t'qlwn 啊 Hisham then khwf those who 不 they reason 'qabh so he said Most High then dmrna alakhryn. 和 indeed you (pl) ltmrwn upon them msbhyn. 和 by night is? fla t'qlwn. 和 said indeed We mnzlwn 'la people of hdhh alqryh rjza 从 the sky bma kanwa they transgress 和 lqd trkna mnha a sign bynh for a people they reason"
